Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.52,0:01:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太阳当空照  朝我微微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun came up and he smiled at me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.85,0:01:23.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说今天真美好  一起等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:23.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Said, "it's gonna be a good one, just wait and see"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳下了床
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumped out of bed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.79,0:01:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,径直跑出门  多欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I ran outside feeling so extra-ecstatified
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.65,0:01:40.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:40.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.70,0:01:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.09,0:01:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你问今天为什么是最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Why is this the best day ever," you ask?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这美好的一天里  要先开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get to start this wonderful day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.53,0:01:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给新一代美味的蟹黄堡带来新生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bringing life to a whole new generation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of delicious Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中午再跟珊迪精力充沛地来场空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Followed by a vigorous midday session
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of karate with Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下午跟派大星捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And an afternoon jellyfishing with Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到那里我会拿出我最新最珍贵的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where I'll unveil my newest, most prized possession
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.60,0:02:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,豪华捉水母复合专业网
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:09.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the deluxe jelly-slayer composite pro
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.82,0:02:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后再来场压轴好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And for the grand finale
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有最亲近的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,every one of my closest friends
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都要一起来欣赏章鱼哥的竖笛演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,joining together for Squidward's clarinet recital
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经兴奋到要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am so excited I think I'm gonna explode
