Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别挡在那里  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王已经被鉴定为危房了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me building's been condemned, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.67,0:03:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里可是闹了一大堆的线虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got ourselves a nematode infestation
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.06,0:03:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.27,0:03:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天应该从蟹堡王开始才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The best day ever starts at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得请你们离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm gonna have to ask you to leave
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ruining the
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.55,0:03:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:35.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best day
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.62,0:03:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best day, um
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续吹  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep playin', lad
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让那些害虫离我蟹堡王远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take the devilish sons of the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,away from me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.71,0:04:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去珊迪家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta get to Sandy's
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.92,0:04:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着让珊迪瞧瞧这双超黏空手道手套
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait till Sandy gets a load of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,these adhesive karate gloves
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you doin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是一点小东西  我管这叫空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a little somethin' I like to call karate
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在没空  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't right now, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屋顶破了个洞  而且大得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a leak in my roof
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the size of a full-grown quarter horse
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧  我等会儿再来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, then, I'll come back later
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.81,0:05:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Off
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.65,0:05:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It stopped?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.15,0:05:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去拿密封胶跟泥铲来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm goin' to get some sealant and patch-n-trowel
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.32,0:05:31.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没蟹黄堡  没空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:31.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No krabby patties, no karate
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但至少还能捉水母  陪着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But at least I still have jellyfishing with-
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他已经在那开捉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he is now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等我  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个全新的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a brand-new
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.14,0:05:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我网断了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I broke my net
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你走运了  我带了我的旧网
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, lucky for you, I brought my old net
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.96,0:05:51.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:51.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我也用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I won't be needin' it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟我有了全新的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now that I got my brand-new
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被我弄断了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I broke
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能用这把吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I use this one?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.58,0:06:05.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我全新的网
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:05.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's my brand-new net
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  现在到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Patrick, it's my turn, now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星老兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, old buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  现在到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's, it's my turn now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来还是音乐会见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll see you at the concert
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.72,0:06:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.09,0:06:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这最美好的一天不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This "best day ever" isn't goin' so good
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没工作  没空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No work, no karate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少还有章鱼哥的音乐会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still have Squidward's concert
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不能让这次机会白白溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't let this one slip through my fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(699.506,367.333)}活动中心隆重介绍\N章鱼哥
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐会全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The concert is ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我簧片坏了  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My reed is shot, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm finished
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together, man
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来听音乐会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I came here for a concert
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管怎样都得让我听到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and darn it, I am gonna get one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我的簧片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But my reed
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.17,0:07:17.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快吹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:17.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now play
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.88,0:07:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.56,0:07:19.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我吹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:19.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said play
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.80,0:07:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快进去  给我来场难忘的音乐会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get in there and give me a concert to remember
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是想去哪  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're goin', kid?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要看章鱼哥吹竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna see Squidward play his clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是我最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's my best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你票呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's your ticket?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一张票马上就来  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One ticket comin' right up, cap'n
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定就在这里面某处的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be in here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have a ticket
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没票禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No ticket, no entry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.80,0:07:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没票禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No ticket, no entry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.05,0:07:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Oh, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have a ticket
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我想看音乐会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I want to go to the show"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"What should I do?"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从后门溜进去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just sneak in the back door"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you are so
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请出示门票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Ticket, please"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门票  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ticket, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Certainly
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回我一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This time I'm gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  你说海绵宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, did you say SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就那个海绵宝宝方裤裤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在贵宾名单里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on the VIP list
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1064,364)}保留
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有保留席
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A reserved seat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在我朋友旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next to my friends
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只要坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is sit down and
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it is not over
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天本来应该是我完美的一天才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This was supposed to be my perfect day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果一切都
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then everything
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.85,0:09:29.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:29.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sit down
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果一切都急转直下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then everything turned to doo-doo
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's OK, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  非常有事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's not OK
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天本该是我最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This was gonna be my best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要先开始做全世界最棒的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Starting with doing the best job in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到蟹堡王上班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,working at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  你帮我解决了危机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, you saved me barnacle
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶跑了那群线虫  保住了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the way you put the run on them nematodes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是后面我本来还要跟珊迪空手道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then I was gonna do karate with Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  可你拯救了树屋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, but you saved the tree dome
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.85,0:09:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我说  还挺酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool, if you ask me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我之后本来要跟派大星去捉水母的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then I was gonna go jellyfishing with Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那时候你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, but then you, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干啥了来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what'd you do, again?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.05,0:10:07.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我不想承认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I hate to admit it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但要是你没修好我的簧片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I suppose if you hadn't fixed my reed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐会肯定就办不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the concert would've been a bust
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.95,0:10:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重点不在于你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not about you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不在于你完美的一天之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or your perfect day or any of those things
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重点在于我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's about us
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  因为你帮了我们大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, and since you did such a good job
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就要补偿你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we wanna make it up to you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟咱说说看  你小小真心有啥愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So just tell us anything your little heart desires
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.98,0:10:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们帮你实现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's yours
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.11,0:10:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚  裤头村音乐演奏家隆重呈现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight, the Bikini Bottom players proudly present
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.40,0:10:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一场超贵演出  主题是最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a very expensive production of the best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好精彩点  花了我不少钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it better be good, for all it's costin' me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:56.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1032,330)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.32,0:10:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的完美工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My perfect job
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.65,0:10:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开启我完美一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Starts my perfect day
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.68,0:11:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后来放松  快活一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then it's time to kick back, relax and play
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不在预算之内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wasn't in the budget
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.42,0:11:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起唱  听歌声美满
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sing along, hear that happy sound
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.60,0:11:20.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别让刺耳音符害你反感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:20.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let those sour notes bring you down
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高潮要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's where it's at
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不报销那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not payin' for that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:34.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1202,342)}最美好的\N一天
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.53,0:11:31.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:31.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.96,0:11:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the best day ever
