Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:46.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.93,0:11:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还得唱多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long do we have to keep this up?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱到他小小真心没力气就好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just till his little heart gives out, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱到他小小真心没力气就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just till his little heart gives out
