Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好朋友节  好朋友节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best friends day, best friends day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好朋友节  好朋友节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best friends day, best friends day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好朋友节快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy best friend-
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这坨口香糖是我最爱的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This chewing gum is my most beloved possession
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.10,0:12:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把它送给我最最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm givin' it to my bestest friend
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当作好朋友节的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on best friends day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的很荣幸  而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Truly honored, and
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你送了我这么神的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got me such an amazing gift
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我送你的却只有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all I got you was
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  我是机宝2.1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, I am robo 2.1
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的贴身机器佣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your personal robot servant
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.42,0:13:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能熟练提供二十五万多种物质享受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am proficient in providing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,over 250,000 creature comforts
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要吃油酥糕点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you care for a pastry?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yum
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又甜又热又多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet, hot and juicy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你这礼物真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, this is a great gift
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your appreciation, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.35,0:13:23.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但它没又大又老又旧的口香糖球好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:23.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's no giant, old, used ball of gum
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别对自己这么苛刻  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be so hard on yourself, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love my gift
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说真的  我现在就要去跟它玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'll go play with it right now
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.32,0:13:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  机宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, robo
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了  派大星主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming, master Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不介意我跟糖糖告别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't mind if I say good-bye to gummy, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not at all
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.04,0:13:41.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:41.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  糖糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, gummy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.66,0:13:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对海绵宝宝好一点  听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You be good to SpongeBob, you hear?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也爱你  糖糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you, too, gummy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他归你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, he's all yours
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既伟大又被人狠狠嚼过的糖糖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,O, majestic and much-masticated gummy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我不配出现在你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,although I am not worthy to be in your presence
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿我的寒舍能令你满意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,may my humble abode please you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真是个大块头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure are a big boy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道要怎么收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know how to handle this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打点空手道就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With a little karate
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.21,0:14:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糖糖  你这摆饰当得可真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gummy, what a beautiful centerpiece you make
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.11,0:14:41.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With your
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.19,0:14:45.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏袜子  和用过的牙刷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:45.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dirty sock, and used toothbrush
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苍蝇  还有发霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,flies, and moldy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.35,0:14:55.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静一点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:55.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get ahold of yourself, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没那么糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not so bad
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟这可是派大星的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all, it is a gift from Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.88,0:15:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.82,0:15:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的礼物必须滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but your gift has got to go
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  臭球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, stink ball
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you never
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, what ya doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他似乎要把糖糖丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It appears that he's throwing gummy away
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么  有这回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, is that true?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会呢  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你要怎么解释这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then how do you explain this?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样的  我喜欢糖糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, I liked gummy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就想着要给它打扮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I decided to dress him up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.45,0:15:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样子是不是很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a cute look?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胆大  却又低调
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bold, yet understated
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好点子  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A brilliant idea, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再接再厉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.75,0:15:54.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  机宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:54.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, robo
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来多找点肚脐眼绒毛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's find more bellybutton lint
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  没派大星的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, no sign of Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better make this fast
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好入土吧  糖糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get ready for your dirt nap, gummy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was digging a hole
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就能更好地欣赏糖糖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I could get a better view of gummy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.66,0:16:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它可真迷人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause he is so attractive
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我来演示一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to demonstrate
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面这个视角可美了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The view is beautiful down here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.52,0:16:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  这视角看它确实挺华丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he does look rather dashing from this angle
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.78,0:16:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糖糖也必须得体大方地放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gummy must be displayed properly and proudly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道放哪里刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I know just the place
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放那边是不是很壮观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't he breath-taking up there?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All righty, SpongeBob, we gotta go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要学着用叉子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna learn how to use a fork
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.97,0:16:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  机宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right, robo?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那将是我的荣幸  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Twill be my pleasure, master
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.65,0:17:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺带一提  你家样子好看了一百万倍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the way, your house looks a million times better
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.97,0:17:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它丑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's hideous
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一厢情愿  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wishful thinking, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪个小偷会想偷那种玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What burglar would want to steal that thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up there?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙儿  我找到出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, I found a way out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.75,0:18:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.05,0:18:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我无糖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sugar-free
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.90,0:19:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  开门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, open up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.83,0:19:12.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:12.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我碰上了一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I got myself into a
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.16,0:19:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黏人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pretty sticky situation
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.54,0:19:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你困在上面多久了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long you been stuck there, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All day
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.50,0:19:27.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的老朋友珊迪会把你砍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:27.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, your old pal Sandy knows how to cut you down
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.06,0:19:27.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:27.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.97,0:19:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.21,0:19:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你越碰它  它就越生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The more you touch it, the angrier it gets
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just crazy talk
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.42,0:19:38.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:38.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Told ya
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自保吧  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save yourself, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃吧  免得你最后的结局变成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run away before you end up like
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  肯定有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, now, there's gotta be a way
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓紧了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all righty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快开啊你  老蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, ol' blue
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许跟我顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you talk back to me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do as you're told
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我听话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, now, do it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是别去管了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just let it go, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别去管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let it go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.50,0:20:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要掺和进去  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't get involved, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm OK
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.88,0:20:55.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:55.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what have you done?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我可以解释
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now Patrick, I can explain
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这  这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's, it's
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像是个糖糖仙境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like a gummy wonderland
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望我能玩得这么快活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I were havin' this much fun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd love it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I have something to tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是否需要按摩  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you care for a massage, master?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.90,0:21:21.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:21.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough already
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说啥了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you were saying something, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.92,0:21:27.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:27.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how can I put this?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有话直说嘛  我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just come right out and-
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you stop?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准闹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just stop
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要说就快说  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get on with it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.70,0:21:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点说完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrap it up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.85,0:21:42.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:42.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.10,0:21:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.37,0:21:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了我  大家都在跟我的糖糖开心玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, everyone is havin' fun with my gummy but me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.93,0:21:50.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我是说你的糖糖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:50.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, I mean your gummy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你想念你的糖糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, do you miss your gummy?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天还是好朋友节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's still best friends day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.29,0:22:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要把糖糖要回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How would you like your gummy back?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.18,0:22:02.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:02.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.85,0:22:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糖糖归你了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's yours, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.76,0:22:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你得先把我们救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But first you gotta get us out of this
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那简单
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.52,0:22:28.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就说很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Told you it was easy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:42.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1154,658)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.65,0:22:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是史上最棒的好朋友节
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the best best friends day ever
